{"tid":845732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上海浦東機場開篋查水貨　逾百代購商排隊繳罰款","createTime":"2018-10-03T01:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T07:48:25.000Z","uid":176442,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7656268d55ceaac3ca191367149ac45892215ed5","tid":845732,"uid":176442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:38:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181002/bkn-20181002194540414-1002_00952_001.html?editorpickDate=20181003&amp;editorpickUuid=402882b15990b2a90159a58b78f0780f&amp;eventid=402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b&amp;eventsection=hk_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181002%2Fbkn-20181002194540414-1002_00952_001.html%3FeditorpickDate%3D20181003%26editorpickUuid%3D402882b15990b2a90159a58b78f0780f%26eventid%3D402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b%26eventsection%3Dhk_news&d=vafsAJtW1FASTd9W%2FbGZwjOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=086b7663\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181002/bkn-20181002194540414-1002_00952_001.html?editorpickDate=20181003&amp;editorpickUuid=402882b15990b2a90159a58b78f0780f&amp;eventid=402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b&amp;eventsection=hk_news</a><br />\n<br />\n內地8月31日推出《電子商務法》，指所有電子商務經營者，包括微商將被責令停業整頓和會被罰款。雖然《電子商務法》明年1月1日實施，惟網絡近日熱傳有內地機場已開始嚴查代購。在上海浦東機場T2航運大樓，上周五（9月28日）所有旅客需全部開行李篋排隊等待過機審查，隊伍長的看不到盡頭。據指有一班航班調查逾百個代購，正排隊等待罰款。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea7fb5a2d15b3779fc38ba39f38a014c3cafd45","tid":845732,"uid":176442,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:39:12.000Z","msg":"據網民指，在被罰的清單中，有最便宜的唇膏，10支Tom Ford唇膏追繳稅項1,800元（約2054港元），3盒面膜被罰200多元（約228港元），還要逐張點算。在開行李過程中，其中一名男旅客突然跪在海關面前。因為他帶了178萬元（人民幣‧下同，約203萬港元）的貨物，情節過於嚴重，交由緝私局調查。<br />\n<br />\n有旅客表示，海關開行李檢查，直到凌晨1時，旅客都要在排隊過機檢查。一眾代購為安全出關，使出渾身解數，求人幫忙帶出去。海關關員只好直接到「源頭」的免稅店調查，但凡是在免稅店購買10多萬元（約11.4萬港元）貨的代購，全部無一幸免。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181002/photo/bkn-20181002194540414-1002_00952_001_02b.jpg?20181002210047\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181002%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181002194540414-1002_00952_001_02b.jpg%3F20181002210047&h=a32bd7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民展示要報稅的單據。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"9f06d255c720c6cabfc04285637852f6a33cb939","tid":845732,"uid":59929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T01:40:47.000Z","msg":"上個月去上海都開始發現過行李嚴格左好多<br />\n原來係打代購"},{"pid":"06172e0c4933a38cc8794f557796b3e42b9a35f4","tid":845732,"uid":24853,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"爽 中共無錢了"},{"pid":"f3465a6966f616b0583666432d22f317be14ca48","tid":845732,"uid":63154,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"中共知民間儲蓄多，宜家等錢駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2580fa27c5c37ef7cae5b180371519df8a747f9f","tid":845732,"uid":179990,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:31:40.000Z","msg":"幾時到羅湖同落馬洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f12effef22669e4b3face147165825cec04e12","tid":845732,"uid":33908,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:33:47.000Z","msg":"去深圳各個關口查仲多啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f39b6869cbc8141e342d26403d0e576395249f3","tid":845732,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06172e0c4933a38cc8794f557796b3e42b9a35f4","tid":845732,"uid":24853,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"爽 中共無錢了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:37:53.000Z","msg":"全面貫徹落實共產主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f83aa963f54e1e62fe07ca785022bc954346cd1","tid":845732,"uid":57329,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T02:43:23.000Z